<h1>坏</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">huài</span><span class=alesi>(huai4)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">pī</span><span class=alesi>(pi1)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">péi</span><span class=alesi>(pei2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 坏 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 坏</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/rotten" style="color:black;">rotten</a>, <a href="/dictionary/spoilt" style="color:black;">spoilt</a>, <a href="/dictionary/bad" style="color:black;">bad</a>, broken down</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/土" title="Kangxi radical 32">土</a>&nbsp;32.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 3 <br><small>Other HSK 3 characters: <a href="/character/闻" title="wen2: hear; smell; make known; news">闻</a>, <a href="/character/换" title="huan4: change">换</a>, <a href="/character/顾" title="gu4: look back; look at; look after">顾</a>, <a href="/character/楚" title="chu3: name of feudal state; clear">楚</a>, <a href="/character/酒" title="jiu3: wine, spirits, liquor, alcoholic beverage">酒</a>, <a href="/character/脚" title="jiao3: leg, foot; base, leg, foundation">脚</a>, <a href="/character/草" title="cao3: grass, straw, thatch, herbs">草</a>, <a href="/character/楼" title="lou2: building of two or more stories">楼</a>, <a href="/character/画" title="hua4: a painting, picture, drawing; to draw">画</a>, <a href="/character/铁" title="tie3: iron; strong, solid, firm">铁</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-3" title="List of HSK 3 char